<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Carrito de Compras</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.5.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container mt-5 text-center">
        <h1>¡Producto agregado al carrito!</h1>
        <p>¿Deseas seguir comprando o finalizar la compra?</p>
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <form method="get" action="/api/products">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">
                        Seguir comprando
                    </button>
                </form>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <form method="post" action="/api/ticket/{{cart._doc._id}}">
                    <input type="hidden" name="cartId" value="{{cart._doc._id}}">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success btn-block">
                        Finalizar compra
                    </button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>

</html>
